[[File:Map of Diplomatic Missions in Botswana.png|thumb|400px|Map of the countries that have diplomatic missions in Botswana.]]
This is a '''list of diplomatic missions in [[Botswana]]''' excluding honorary consulates. The capital [[Gaborone]] currently hosts 19 embassies and 3<ref>Honorary Consulate of Greece </ref> consulates. The city is also host to several international organizations. Most of the diplomatic missions that cover Botswana are in [[South Africa]].<ref name=mofaic>{{cite web|url=http://www.mofaic.gov.bw/|date=2010-06-23|accessdate=2010-06-27|title=Botswana Ministry of Foreign Affairs and International Cooperation|author=Ministry of Foreign Affairs and International Cooperation|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100418173433/http://www.mofaic.gov.bw/|archivedate=2010-04-18|df=}}</ref>

